OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cblackmail plot to cover gambling debt
OL,6,FA former police officer who posed as a
OL,7,Fpaedophile hunter and tried to
OL,8,Fblackmail a suspect to cover her
OL,9,Fgambling debts has been jailed.
OL,11,FPC Marie Thompson, 29, was a police
OL,12,Fconstable in Doncaster at the time.
OL,14,FShe was in charge of a South Yorkshire
OL,15,FPolice investigation into a man whom
OL,16,Fshe arrested in 2022, on suspicion of
OL,17,Fpossessing indecent images of children.
