OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cblackmail plot to cover gambling debt
OL,6,FThe man was interviewed and released
OL,7,Funder investigation before receiving
OL,8,Fam email demanding #3,500 be paid into
OL,9,Fa bank account signed "Paedophile
OL,10,FHunters".
OL,12,FShe told the the suspect the
OL,13,Fallegations would be kept a secret if
OL,14,Fhe paid the ransom.
OL,16,FThe email said the payment would
OL,17,F"ensure that information remains
OL,18,Fbetween you and us".
