OL,6,FLater the same day, the man's partner
OL,7,Freceived a text message saying that a
OL,8,Freply was needed by the end of the day.
OL,10,FThe man refused to hand over the money
OL,11,Fand instead reported it to South
OL,12,FYorkshire Police, and the
OL,13,Finvestigation was allocated to
OL,14,FThompson.
OL,16,FThompson tried to cover her tracks by
OL,17,Ffalsely noting the man did not want to
OL,18,Ftake any further action.
