OL,6,FSix weeks later, she also told the man
OL,7,Fshe was unable to find out who was
OL,8,Fresponsible for sending the blackmail
OL,9,Femail and text.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police said an
OL,12,Finvestigation was launched when
OL,13,Fsuspicions were raised about Thompson,
OL,14,Fwho was still in her probation period
OL,15,Fwith the force.
OL,17,FThe court heard the emails had been
OL,18,Fsent from her personal laptop, and
OL,19,Fthat she was in significant debt
OL,20,Fthrough gambling.
