OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cblackmail plot to cover gambling debt
OL,6,FShe was arrested in October 2023 and
OL,7,Fsuspended from duties. She resigned
OL,8,Ffrom the force on October 2025.
OL,10,FThompson pleaded guilty to blackmail
OL,11,Fan perverting the course of justice,
OL,12,Fand was jailed for 40 months on
OL,13,FThursday.
OL,15,FDetective Constable Alexandra Furniss
OL,16,Fsaid the former police officer's
OL,17,Fcrimes were "shameful."
